Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TextCN,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Avant--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.00,TextCN,,0,0,0,,这什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:14.81,TextCN,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:16.70,TextCN,,0,0,0,,请让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.44,TextCN,,0,0,0,,我叫刚田猛男 今年高一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:38.76,TextCN,,0,0,0,,这是第一次 我喜欢的女生也喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.52,TextCN,,0,0,0,,我有了第一个女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:48.20,TextCN,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:52.57,TextCN,,0,0,0,,好喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:56.09,TextCN,,0,0,0,,那个 我们还是第一次在电车里见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:58.56,TextCN,,0,0,0,,你一直坐这趟电车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:00:59.47,TextCN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:02.29,TextCN,,0,0,0,,我以后要不要也坐这趟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.47,TextCN,,0,0,0,,但是这样的话 时间有些紧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:09.88,TextCN,,0,0,0,,虽然很想和你一起 但也不能迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.07,TextCN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:12.47,TextCN,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:17.14,TextCN,,0,0,0,,也是呢 迟到总是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.17,TextCN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,0)}那对情侣好彪悍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.47,TextCN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,0)}不不 是父女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:17.88,TextCN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,0)}但那大叔 穿着校服啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TextCN,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Part A--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:04.91,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,420)}我　很　迟　钝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:06.21,TextCN,,0,0,0,,接着昨天的内容 把书翻到24页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.36,TextCN,,0,0,0,,栗原同学 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.21,TextCN,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.87,TextCN,,0,0,0,,好 翻到24页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.44,TextCN,,0,0,0,,我早上看到好东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.36,TextCN,,0,0,0,,看得我都兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.68,TextCN,,0,0,0,,要是我肯定就来个初吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.59,TextCN,,0,0,0,,猛男不会做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.82,TextCN,,0,0,0,,猛男不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.38,TextCN,,0,0,0,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.57,TextCN,,0,0,0,,然后 他们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.98,TextCN,,0,0,0,,关门请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:42.10,TextCN,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 我要下车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:42.92,TextCN,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.58,TextCN,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.56,TextCN,,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.56,TextCN,,0,0,0,,猛男一个人坐过了站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:01.67,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H989F69&\1a&H00&\pos(950,244)}好 棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:01.67,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H81724D&\1a&H00&\pos(778,605)}太　感　人　了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H979E6D&\1a&H00&\pos(778,162)}太　感　人　了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.94,TextCN,,0,0,0,,太帅了 忍不住拍了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:11.95,TextCN,,0,0,0,,猛男好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.40,TextCN,,0,0,0,,这是特快电车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\b0\fs30\frz352\pos(1130,65)\1a&H64&}好　酷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.21,TextCN,,0,0,0,,他一个人坐到终点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.41,TextCN,,0,0,0,,话说这女孩为什么会喜欢刚田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.02,TextCN,,0,0,0,,她明明那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:19.86,TextCN,,0,0,0,,就是啊
